items.title: Nodule found in former President Biden's prostate during routine physical exam
items.description: A small nodule was found in the prostate of former President Joseph R. Biden during a routine physical exam, a spokesperson said Tuesday.

items.title: U.S., Saudi Arabia sign economic partnership pact
items.description: President Trump and Saudi Crown Prince Mohammed bin Salman signed a strategic economic partnership agreement in Riyadh on Tuesday.

items.title: Supreme Court Chief Justice Roberts says rule of law is 'endangered'
items.description: Supreme Court Chief Justice John G. Roberts Jr. suggested Monday the rule of law is "endangered" during remarks in Washington.
